OL,3,CTravel warnings issued in Crete as
OL,4,Cdust storm turns skies bright red
OL,6,FIntense storms across Greece have
OL,7,Fkilled one man close to Athens and
OL,8,Fturned the skies of Crete bright red.
OL,10,FStorm Erminio swept across Greece on
OL,11,FWednesday, causing gale-force winds
OL,12,Fand extreme flooding which halted
OL,13,Ftravel and damaged roads and buildings.
OL,15,FA Polish man, reported to be in his
OL,16,F50s, was killed in Nea Makri, north-
OL,17,Feast of Athens, after he became
OL,18,Ftrapped under a vehicle in rushing
OL,19,Fflood water, the fire department said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
