OL,3,CTravel warnings issued in Crete as
OL,4,Cdust storm turns skies bright red
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThere were 674 calls for help from
OL,12,FWednesday overnight into Thursday, the
OL,13,Fmajority of which were in the Attica
OL,14,Fregion, which includes Athens.
OL,16,FEmergency services were seen clearing
OL,17,Fdebris, repairing damaged
OL,18,Finfrastructure and pumping water out
OL,19,Fof flooded buildings on Thursday
OL,20,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
