OL,3,CTravel warnings issued in Crete as
OL,4,Cdust storm turns skies bright red
OL,6,FA red weather warning is in place
OL,7,Funtil late Thursday evening, with
OL,8,Fmultiple flights and ferries cancelled
OL,9,Fover the impaired visibility.
OL,11,FA British Airways flight to Crete from
OL,12,FLondon was rerouted to Corfu, and a
OL,13,FSky Express flight from Brussels
OL,14,Flanded in Athens.
OL,16,FSailing is banned, and no ships are
OL,17,Fdeparting from the island port of
OL,18,FSouda or the mainland port of Piraeus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
